{"tid":1492811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有Twitter嘅入黎同我report呢個日本五毛","createTime":"2019-08-21T04:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:02:51.000Z","uid":44298,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"918ed067dca3072dbed602f813a973e7e7abb71d","tid":1492811,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:01:39.000Z","msg":"香港メールニュース (@hkmailnews)：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkmailnews?s=08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkmailnews%3Fs%3D08&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41Hs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=8fc8c334\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkmailnews?s=08</a><br />\n<br />\n佢原本係做一本香港俾日本人睇嘅免費雜誌，本雜誌收左皮，而家搞網上版。用香港揾食，但係佢嘅post全部都係鬧香港示威。鬧示威者嘅日本五毛好多，唔好同佢地嘈希望大家report到佢地收皮。<br />\n<br />\n教學：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97JWSWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97JWSWE.jpg&h=8488ae10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBsHOu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBsHOu7.jpg&h=32743b6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c08e56a6e9af32d831236dc14c6d0733b3693178","tid":1492811,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:03:46.000Z","msg":"done"},{"pid":"39bbc5996c22f9997b8731410d76890e242e9ab5","tid":1492811,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:08:17.000Z","msg":"report死日本五毛"},{"pid":"f6e54f39ff9e3bbe97b8e9fae5df072d42238586","tid":1492811,"uid":68216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"有無巴打 整合下 香港係點樣比中共一步一步滲透同各方面控制丫 整合一個中文版 再由其他巴打翻譯 比外國人睇到<br />\n<br />\n［國際文宣］用英文整合中共係國際各個層面唧控制 令外國人都會有身受其害嘅覺悟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1492342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1492342</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47d08e111eb7d5b7c5e424d0593eb82047036165","tid":1492811,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl